<subSubSection pageId="50" pageNumber="51" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="50" pageNumber="51">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="50" pageNumber="51">
Holotype unknown. The type locality is South Africa, Cape of Good Hope (Serville coll.). According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Kimsey, LS" journalOrPublisher="University Press, New York" pageId="73" pageNumber="74" title="The Chrysidid Wasps of the World." year="1991">Kimsey and Bohart (1991</bibRefCitation>
: 387), the holotype should be housed in the Spinola collection, but we could not find any evidence for this assumption. The type should be searched for at MNHN.
</paragraph>
